{
  "text": "The VG antibody is described and antibody staining was performed according to a published protocol [CITATION_1] , and was visualized using a Leica TCS confocal microscope. The anti-SENS antibody was used as described in [CITATION_2] . Mouse anti-WG antibody was obtained from the Developmental Studies Hybridoma Bank, University of Iowa. Anti-PH3 antibody was from Upstate Biotech and has been previously described [CITATION_3] . Secondary antibodies were anti-rabbit Alexa 488 from Molecular Probes and Cy3 conjugated anti-rabbit, antiguinea pig and anti-mouse IgG from Jackson Immunoresearch. ",
